#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.172"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.172:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.172:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga"
msgstr "18. Intention"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sāriputta-paṭisambhidāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.172:0.3"
msgid "172. Vibhattisutta"
msgstr "172. Sāriputta’s Attainment of Textual Analysis"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.172:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There Sāriputta addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an4.172:1.2"
msgid "“āvuso bhikkhave”ti."
msgstr "“Reverends, mendicants!”"

msgctxt "an4.172:1.3"
msgid "“Āvuso”ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Reverend,” they replied."

msgctxt "an4.172:1.4"
msgid "Āyasmā sāriputto etadavoca:"
msgstr "Sāriputta said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.172:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, atthapaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso "
"byañjanaso."
msgstr ""
"“Reverends, I realized the textual analysis of the meaning—piece by piece "
"and expression by expression—a fortnight after I ordained."

msgctxt "an4.172:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi "
"vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi."
msgstr ""
"In many ways I explain, teach, assert, establish, clarify, analyze, and "
"reveal it."

msgctxt "an4.172:2.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena."
msgstr "Whoever has any doubt or uncertainty, let them ask me,"

msgctxt "an4.172:2.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo."
msgstr ""
"I will answer. Our teacher is present, he who is so very skilled in our "
"teachings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.172:3.1"
msgid ""
"Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, dhammapaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso "
"byañjanaso."
msgstr ""
"I realized the textual analysis of the text—piece by piece and expression by "
"expression—a fortnight after I ordained. …"

msgctxt "an4.172:3.2"
msgid ""
"Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi "
"vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.172:3.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.172:3.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.172:4.1"
msgid ""
"Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, niruttipaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso "
"byañjanaso."
msgstr ""
"I realized the textual analysis of terminology—piece by piece and expression "
"by expression—a fortnight after I ordained. …"

msgctxt "an4.172:4.2"
msgid ""
"Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi "
"vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.172:4.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.172:4.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.172:5.1"
msgid ""
"Addhamāsūpasampannena me, āvuso, paṭibhānapaṭisambhidā sacchikatā odhiso "
"byañjanaso."
msgstr ""
"I realized the textual analysis of eloquence—piece by piece and expression "
"by expression—a fortnight after I ordained."

msgctxt "an4.172:5.2"
msgid ""
"Tamahaṃ anekapariyāyena ācikkhāmi desemi paññāpemi paṭṭhapemi vivarāmi "
"vibhajāmi uttānīkaromi."
msgstr ""
"In many ways I explain, teach, assert, establish, clarify, analyze, and "
"reveal it."

msgctxt "an4.172:5.3"
msgid "Yassa kho panassa kaṅkhā vā vimati vā, so maṃ pañhena."
msgstr "If anyone has any doubt or uncertainty, let them ask me,"

msgctxt "an4.172:5.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ veyyākaraṇena sammukhībhūto no satthā yo no dhammānaṃ sukusalo”ti."
msgstr ""
"I will answer. Our teacher is present, he who is so very skilled in our "
"teachings.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.172:5.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
